&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://archive.org/download/Islam_enmity_against_Science/muslim_scientists/muslim_scientists-page-002.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;1275&quot; height=&quot;1275&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
